{"tid":1722614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水藍絲伯伯死左，真係好可憐！好慘！無陰公！","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T07:58:52.000Z","uid":202464,"like":47,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cb075c8dfce05862b4f43be07128277554681423","tid":1722614,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"前晚（13日）天水圍警署外，15 歲傅同學疑被催淚彈射中頭，顱骨骨折。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，傅同學手術紀錄為槍傷，現時情況仍然危殆，昏迷指數只有3分，「即係眼無張開、插喉、對痛楚無知覺反應。」<br />\n<br />\n在現場為傅同學急救的何先生透露，當時傅同學頭頂正中間偏右後流血，右腿大髀上方亦有懷疑被催淚彈射中、3 至 4 級燒傷的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n傅同學的母親數年前因胃癌離世，父親在三年前亦患病離世，自此便與哥哥相依為命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊撚個左膠仲要話上水阿伯慘既，落地獄啦！</span>"},{"pid":"8d4113a4939acbe1e1907a631a748a7a4c9ea1e9","tid":1722614,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勿推</span>"},{"pid":"8079933fa010c9ddf77d87e820099ddd2e2fe677","tid":1722614,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12bd0579ce7597ebe1f6216ff40b4de37893563","tid":1722614,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4629bcb8672cec131ed0080e8ef9f9c03b839d22","tid":1722614,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:03:47.000Z","msg":